## ESP32-WROVER Cam

A cam to catch a fleet-footed feathered friend who visit my bird-feeder.

*rev001*: Baseline, access ESP32-WROVER cam via web with vendor-supplied web-server library.
*rev002*: Add feature to capture image every sec and encode in base64.
*rev003*: Send to Hive MQTT broker and verify transmission.
*rev004*: Send Telegram notification when motion is detected (w simulated sensor).
*rev005*: Add feature for motion detection by sensor.
